headtouch: Headpats, headpatty pat, patty patty head, heady heady pat pat~ Ahahah!
battle: I don't want to do this... but you leave me no choice!
mission_complete: Bingo, this looks great. Commander, we've received stellar rewards!
touch2: Hahah, I know how much you enjoy doing lewd things like this.
mission: Let's see here... I think you should review these missions.
feeling5: You know everything about me, from my horns to my personality. Since we're so intimate, I suppose it's needless to tell you... Actually, there's one thing I want to tell you: I will NOT go along with your flirting when we're in the office!
home: Welcome back. As much as I want you to be successful, I'm just as happy with everything staying the way it is.
main: Too much work to process? We all know what a tough job it is to command a fleet. So please, let me give you some assistance.|We are who we are now thanks to you, Commander. And while not everyone respects you, they are grateful for what you do. You really should be proud of yourself for that. I-I feel more for you than just respect, though!|I don't mind fading into the background when I'm with my friends, but when I'm with you, I want everyone to see it. Heheh, in a friendly way, of course.|Once the war has ended, then we can discuss everything we'll do once the war ends. For now, we must focus all our efforts on fighting to eventually achieve peace.
login: Don't be afraid to ask for my help if you need it. It is, after all, a secretary's job to support her Commander.
detail: I've said it time and time again: I'm not fit to be the joint exercise flagship or for any other prominent position! Why won't they listen when I say I'd screw it up horribly?! ...C-Commander?! Oh, ahh...

feeling5: I-I wasn't expecting you to actually carry me around the port... I'm stunned... Listen, I don't mind being with you, but stop treating me like baby!

detail: I'm so glad we finally can be together, Ariake! All that time I spent worrying about when I'd be able to see you seems like a distant illusion now…

mission_complete: Attention: confirmation required for mission rewards. Wow...!
touch: I'm waiting for any order you may have, Master.
touch2: Body temperature abnormality detected. Master, what's happening to me...?
home: Here is a glass of armagnac, if you'd like.
feeling5: I've studied many emotions, worries, and hopes during my time in this fleet... Now I finally understand what you expect of me, Master. Thank you so, so much, Master...
mission: Attention: confirmation required for incomplete missions. Master...?
main: "Raise the corners of your lips"... Executing order. L-like this...? I may be doing it wrong...|Analysis complete. Master is in a state of "slacking off." Slacking off is not good.|"Do whatever you want"... Master, how am I meant to do "whatever"...?|Discrepancy detected between the information in my core and the members of the fleet. Why does everyone smile?
expedition: Attention: confirmation required for commission team's return. Whew...
mail: Attention: confirmation required for new mail. A-ahem!
detail: Analyzing armaments... Condition: satisfactory. Please inform me if you have any orders, Master.

feeling5: 主人，您已经足够优秀了，我对此感到很骄傲。不过请放心，一旦出现了新的问题，我会继续帮主人您指出来的。

touch: Your gaze makes me feel odd, Master...
touch2: I'm sorry, Master... My body feels strangely warm...
login: Welcome back, Master. I'm attempting to do "whatever I want"...
detail: Permission to inspect me...? R-right now...?
home: I have prepared us some water and food... Would you like some, Master?
main: The summer winds... Master, is this what "relaxation" feels like...?|This crab seems to be saying "hello, I'm a crab!" ...Does what I said work as a "joke"?|"Let's go for a swim" – I'll go get a swimg ring... Master, are you sure I "don't need one"?
unlock: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Master, what things do you do to "have fun on the beach"...?

mission_complete: Commander, do you want your mission rewards or do you want me? You have to choose! ... Hehe, just kidding~
touch: Commander, don't you think Veneto looks a bit dim, cool as she might be?
touch2: Commander, should I be angry? Positively inconsolable?
home: Commander, I'm going to catch a few winks on the sofa here. Wake me up if anyone comes calling.
mission: Big Brother, I finished organizing your mission list ♪ ... Hehe, is that your type, Commander?
main: That Ajax, she saw straight through me right away... And yet, I think we get along rather well. I've learned a lot from her.|Haah... I'm back. Those tea parties have some delicious snacks, sure, but they're so dreadfully uptight about bearing and deportment.... Hehehe, Commander, would you mind helping me with my shoes?|Commander, which of my sisters is more your type? The sweet and gentle Illustrious, or the passionate Victorious?
expedition: Ding dong ding dong ♪, incoming message from Formidable: Commission complete. Repeat. Commission complete.
mail: Commander, the mail is here. Would you mind getting it yourself?
login: You're late, Commander. I've been waiting for ages!
detail: The posters on the walls are all my favourite rock stars. I don't usually let anyone see them. You're a special exception, Commander~

mission: Hurry up and finish the new missions. Otherwise, people will say that I'm not carrying out my duties as secretary ship.
win_mvp: Fantastic! We won!! ...What is it?! Am I not allowed to be proud of our accomplishments?
login: You've kept me waiting this whole time... Commander, have you not eaten yet? Sh-shall I prepare something for you?
main: nil|Commander, wouldn't it be best to ask for others' opinions every once in a while? I'm not the jealous type, you know.|I pledged to bring you victory, so please sortie me more often! ...I, I also want to attain victory for my own sake as well!
